{"tid":1515874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［代post］830 一齊唱歌向勇武義士致敬","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T18:17:09.000Z","uid":240968,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf045ff8a43af3e9fa2929dabf5730d391c2d9c","tid":1515874,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>緊急！！！！！！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人2個半對抗邪惡政權既抗戰中，<br />\n唔少手足被人拉 ，被人羞辱 ，<br />\n甚至有義士付出生命，<br />\n因此幾日前有巴打作左 抗爭者軍曲<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">《願榮光歸香港》</span></span><br />\n比各勇武和理非手足  誓不屈服既香港人<br />\n<br />\n試幻想係未來香港真 . 重光紀念日聽到黎首軍歌，你一定<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">起雞皮喊出黎</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（包括我同好多巴絲打）<br />\n<br />\n我宜家誠徵各位手足係<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">830感謝勇武暨重光紀念日</span></span><br />\n大家一齊大合唱，<br />\n意指<br />\n1）向留血留淚，付出生命既義士致敬<br />\n2）提升提高勇武士氣，831更多人出黎<br />\n3）向國際宣揚香港人自由意志<br />\n4）向支共港共展現香港人既決心<br />\n<br />\n想幫手手足，入Google留TG ID！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=9c67f95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">教學板</span></span><br />\n（邊帶著headphone聽，邊錄音）<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdgx-dgx%2Fanthem&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ea92437f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem</a><br />\n<br />\n首歌由Dgx巴打同團隊一齊編曲<br />\n結集巴絲打既智慧下出埋埋歌詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通用版歌詞:<br />\nA1<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\nA2<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\n通用版 B<br />\n在 晚星 墜落 徬徨 午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處 吹 來 號 角 聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也 永不滅<br />\n<br />\nA3<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為勝利 時代革命 <br />\n祈求 民主 與自由 萬世都 不朽<br />\n我願 榮光 歸香港<br />\n<br />\n10人Mix<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-test9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdgx-dgx%2Fanthem-test9&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=76af6ae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-test9</a><br />\n<br />\n純音樂<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdgx-dgx%2Fanthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=15918126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t</a><br />\n<br />\nYoutube 字幕版 純音樂 <br />\n(為正義 變為勝利)<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KHY_Nsrm8qU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKHY_Nsrm8qU&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=bc604ced\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KHY_Nsrm8qU</a><br />\n<br />\nOrgan 管風琴版 <br />\nBy 高學歷廢青巴打<br />\n（好神聖高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽完再喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dr-rubbish-teen/hong-kong-anthem-organ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdr-rubbish-teen%2Fhong-kong-anthem-organ&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=ca14be94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dr-rubbish-teen/hong-kong-anthem-organ</a><br />\n<br />\n之後會有新音樂<br />\n同百人合唱version，<br />\n請mon post/ subscribe/<br />\n支持巴打團隊<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>抗爭者軍曲《願榮光歸香港》6人合唱版!!!!  招唱招樂手!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1515087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1515087</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">誠招巴絲打獻聲</span></strong></span><br />\n另外，<br />\nDgx巴打團隊錄緊通用版百人合唱版，<br />\n緊急需要手足幫手唱錄音<br />\n- 錄 純人聲版 上載至 soundcloud<br />\n（上載時記得禁public or download，Dgx巴先down到黎用）<br />\n- Copy條link去 <a href=\"https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=9c67f95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8</a><br />\n- 大家可以試下唱得激昂D <br />\n- 跟住上面錄通用版先<br />\n- B段 迷霧裡 最遠處 最遠處 <br />\n係拖耐D先入（聽上面示範）<br />\n- A3段 唱 同行兒女 為勝利 時代革命<br />\n- 尾句 香港 個港字 係滑音，由江滑到港音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>招Helper</strong></span></span><br />\n想做合唱團/軍樂團/MIXING/<br />\n幫手既人都可以係google留TG ID聯絡，<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=9c67f95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XLCnYwWNq2B7Jkqw8</a>"},{"pid":"c21ad7809c40a6c32bf7d228504a1ce5e1f18d05","tid":1515874,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:43:58.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"b64e77deaf9aa4677ab5bcd8b9047e6860b44bcc","tid":1515874,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"